{
  "stem": "19969.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 90.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I don't-- I don't agree with the Muslim religion or the Buddhist, either, but I respect they believe in it and they may be right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "None of us know, that's the problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- we're convinced that we're Jewish or Christian, that we have the only religion-- the only true religion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, other people feel the same way about their religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I am not going to criticize them because they don't feel the same way that I do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's the message I try to get across in the speeches that I make.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Race, religion, or intolerance has no place in this world and we-- I say we've made a lot of strides, but we're far from perfect in that field and probably never will be.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I spoke at the dedication of the Holocaust Museum, I guess it was last-- last year.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was one of the four speakers who spoke at that-- they had a tremendous event there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is a tremendous institution, that Holocaust Memorial Museum.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was amazed at how-- what a tremendous amount of work and money that has gone to constructing that museum.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's right in downtown Washington and it's run by the National Parks Service.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you want to see that, it takes a good three or four hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You've got to last-- I would say not less than three hours to see all the exhibits that they have.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If anybody who says it didn't happen goes through that museum, I don't know how they can say that all that was fabricated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, your mind has got to go-- take a crazy turn to believe that it never happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I talked to one of the museum people last week.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
